promptPrefix: Give me a list of target keywords for a business-to-business company website site seeking to rank high on Google for [PROMPT]. Please return a table including the keywords, search intent, keyword cluster, a sample content topic for each, and an outline of each sample content topic. Also indicate what type of content would work best for the specific keyword (e.g., a blog post, a white paper, a guide or a video). Return results in [TARGETLANGUAGE].
title: Keyword Strategy
